univention-xrdp (2.0.0-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * Bump version for UCC 2.0 (Bug #29893)
  * Update copyright
  * Update for xrdp 0.8 upstream packages:
    - Update file behind /etc/default/xrdp template
    - Drop template for /etc/init.d/xrdp
    - Update /etc/pam.d/sesman-xrdp for upstream changes
    - Update template for /etc/xrdp/sesman-rdp.ini (drop xrdp/dpi which is unused
      and only applicable for the VNC backend)
    - Update template for /etc/xrdp/xrdp.ini (drop xrdp/title and xrdp/imagedir,
      the login screen is implemented in GDI code in the new release)
    - Update dependencies
  * Add a session script for UCC KDE, make the session script configurable using
    the UCR variable xrdp/desktopsession
  * Make the logo shown during xrdp login configurable with the UCR variable xrdp/logo
  * Enable xrdp init scripts (it ships an init script, but it's not enabled)

 -- Moritz MÃ¼hlenhoff <muehlenhoff@univention.de>  Tue, 08 Apr 2014 09:01:49 +0200

